Class GeoprocessTree

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
IGeoprocessTree, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.ScrollPaneConstants
public class GeoprocessTree
extends javax.swing.JScrollPane
implements IGeoprocessTree

This component shows all registered geoprocesses in extension point "GeoprocessManager", in a tree style. Its different subnodes represents an organization of geoprocesses. Leaf nodes are IGeoprocessPlugin instances.

azabala
